&lt;p&gt;There is a part time Staff Nurse vacancy within our busy Outpatient Department, also covering sessions in both South Pembrokeshire Hospital and Tenby Cottage Hospital.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and motivated people to join our team. The successful candidate will support clinics within the Outpatient service. Full induction into the area will be given.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held 24th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
